Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.66,0:00:19.37,Sign,PHONE,0,0,0,,Mitaka Jin
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:25.00,Sign,PAPER,0,0,0,,Letter of Exam Success
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:32.88,Saku-main,MAID,0,0,0,,Misaki-sama cannot come \Nto the phone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:34.26,Saku-main,MAID,0,0,0,,Please leave a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.62,0:00:41.41,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.12,0:00:43.40,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,What should I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.08,0:02:19.70,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,This is the place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:28.12,Eptitle,EPTITLE,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,1)}#18 First Love with an Alien
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:35.30,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0,0,0,,Thanks for meeting me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:40.30,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0,0,0,,I'm taking the afternoon \Nflight to San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:41.72,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,For work?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:45.00,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm supposed to give a \Npresentation at a game conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.73,0:02:47.29,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0,0,0,,So, shall we get started?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.29,0:02:49.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:53.15,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:02:56.90,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0,0,0,,Let's move forward with \Nyour idea for the battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.27,0:02:58.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.39,0:03:03.65,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0,0,0,,Now, we just have to write up a \Npitch for the title review board.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:05.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:06.34,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:08.38,Saku-main,,0,0,0,,Could we ask the girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:10.81,Saku-main,,0,0,0,,who drew this to do some \Nadditional illustrations for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.18,0:03:13.53,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0,0,0,,It has such presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:17.57,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0,0,0,,I think including more drawings would \Nhelp us with the review board.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:20.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:22.76,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0,0,0,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:26.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,No, I'll ask Shiina about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:27.95,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0,0,0,,Then, let's call it a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:29.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.76,0:03:31.55,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0,0,0,,Planning to go on a date after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:35.06,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,The results of my sister's \Nexam come out this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:36.77,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:39.28,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:43.53,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Huh? Sensei, you're \Nworking again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:45.93,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0,0,0,,I have a meeting I don't want to go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.73,0:03:49.81,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:53.77,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Usually she says something like, \N"Why don't you go in my place?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:55.83,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,Kanda-kun, you're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:03:57.18,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm home...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.56,0:03:59.34,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,But I'm changing and heading \Nstraight back out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.89,0:04:01.38,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,For Yuko-chan's test results, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.89,0:04:03.27,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,Can I go with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.27,0:04:03.95,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.95,0:04:05.34,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,Wait right here. I'll go get changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:07.53,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:09.90,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Why did you tag along, Shiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:12.12,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0,0,0,,Whether Yuko passes or not is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:12.94,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:15.00,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0,0,0,,It's related to my plans for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:16.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,What happens if she passes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:17.98,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0,0,0,,Plan C.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:19.48,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,You really like that plan, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.02,0:04:20.99,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0,0,0,,Do you prefer Plan B?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:22.92,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,That's the one where we go out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:24.20,Saku-overlap,NANAMI,0,0,0,,G-Go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:24.20,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,N-No, it's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:26.16,Saku-thought,NAMAMI,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:28.58,Saku-thought,SORATA,0,0,0,,A-Aoyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.93,0:04:34.92,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0,0,0,,Sorata, Nanami... \NYour faces are red. Are you sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:36.58,Saku-main,BOTH,0,0,0,,N-No, we're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:38.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Come on, let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:45.71,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,B-By the way, Aoyama, when do the \Nresults of your audition come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:48.85,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,B-Between the end of February \Nand the middle of March.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:49.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:51.52,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0,0,0,,Sorata, you seem happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:52.63,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,How do I look happy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:53.65,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,Nanami, you seem happy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.65,0:04:55.15,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,Th-That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.15,0:04:56.07,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0,0,0,,Not that I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:04:57.96,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Then, don't act like you're angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:04:59.30,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0,0,0,,I'm not angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:00.59,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,She sounds it, doesn't she, Aoyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:01.21,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:04.11,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0,0,0,,You're being friendly with Nanami again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:05.67,Saku-main,BOTH,0,0,0,,N-No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:05.67,Saku-overlap,NANAMI,0,0,0,,N-No, he's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:06.86,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0,0,0,,See? Friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:09.21,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,I-It's green.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.21,0:05:10.53,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:12.96,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,O-Oh, I forgot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:14.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Shiina, I have a favor to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:15.39,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:16.66,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Would you draw more illustrations for—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:17.38,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.84,0:05:21.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,But if it'll get in the way of your manga—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:21.05,Saku-overlap,MASHIRO,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:23.63,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,I-I see. In that case, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:25.88,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0,0,0,,Sorata, you're not happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:29.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,No, that's not it. It's a huge help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:30.55,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0,0,0,,Then, I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.05,0:05:36.39,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,What's Yuko-chan's number?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:38.28,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Ninety-nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:40.90,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:48.49,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Well, not much we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:52.79,Saku-main,YUKO,0,0,0,,How did it go, Onii-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:53.62,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,You failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:55.52,Saku-main,YUKO,0,0,0,,That's impossible! Check again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:57.18,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,No matter how many times I \Ncheck, you still failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:06:00.56,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,All the other numbers in the nineties \Npassed, but 99 isn't up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:01.92,Saku-main,YUKO,0,0,0,,Why only me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:04.59,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,You must not have scored \Nvery well on the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:07.84,Saku-main,YUKO,0,0,0,,Why can't you be nicer \Nto me when I'm in pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:11.53,Saku-main,YUKO,0,0,0,,When can I crack open my ball with the \N"congratulations on passing" banner?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.53,0:06:13.14,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,How should I know? And what \Nthe heck is that, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:14.95,Saku-main,YUKO,0,0,0,,I pulled three all-nighters making it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:16.07,Saku-main,YUKO,0,0,0,,I'm breaking it open now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:18.30,Saku-main,YUKO,0,0,0,,My ball failed, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:20.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Do your best on the \Nprefectural school exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:22.66,Saku-main,SAORI,0,0,0,,Kanda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:25.29,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:28.40,Saku-main,SAORI,0,0,0,,My younger brother, Iori, \Napplied to the music department.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:29.36,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:31.20,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:32.53,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:33.28,Saku-main,SAORI,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:37.08,Saku-main,SAORI,0,0,0,,Looks like Misaki isn't with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:37.62,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:40.60,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0,0,0,,Mitaka's here at the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:41.96,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Huh? Jin-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:45.79,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0,0,0,,He came to tell his homeroom \Nteacher that he passed his exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:50.01,Saku-main,SAORI,0,0,0,,Mitaka really intends to leave \NMisaki behind and go to Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:52.69,Saku-main,SAORI,0,0,0,,She didn't even get to see \Nhim on Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:55.83,Saku-main,SAORI,0,0,0,,There are only two weeks \Nleft before graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:57.77,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Two weeks...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:07:00.74,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,I can't believe the two of \Nthem will graduate like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:03.56,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,They can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:06.93,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Aoyama! Misaki-senpai—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:07.98,Saku-main,AOYAMA,0,0,0,,I'll go back and get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:10.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Thanks! I'll keep Jin-san from leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:16.15,Saku-main,SAORI,0,0,0,,Do you think it'll be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:19.25,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0,0,0,,Who knows? I can't look \Nafter them all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:26.38,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,If you'll excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:28.06,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Jin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:29.06,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:31.17,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,Mashiro-chan, that's some \Nface you're pulling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:32.68,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Could you come with us for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:35.10,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,It's forbidden love.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:42.11,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,Fine, fine. Do whatever \Nyou want with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:45.52,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,Why did you bring me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:48.99,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,You're not actually confessing \Nyour love to me, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:50.44,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,It's about Misaki-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:53.86,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,How has she been lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:56.03,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0,0,0,,She's making an animation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:58.06,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,That's what she should be doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.46,0:08:00.29,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,She'll forget about me soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.78,0:08:02.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:04.08,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,Would it be better if \NI said I was joking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:05.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:08.38,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,I'm going to Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:11.16,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Please talk to Misaki-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:13.34,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,I can't date Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:14.22,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Jin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:16.70,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,What else am I supposed to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:18.90,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,You're not acting like your usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:20.43,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,And what's my usual self?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:23.84,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Always cool, always smart, \Ncapable of anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.84,0:08:26.31,Saku-main,,0,0,0,,mature, dependable, \Nand always gives me advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:28.73,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,That's the person I expect you to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.37,0:08:32.49,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,You're mistaken. Give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:34.57,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,I can't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:38.33,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,How can you think I'd give \Nup on you and Misaki-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:39.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:41.34,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,What if someone takes \NMisaki-senpai away from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:41.12,Saku-overlap,JIN,0,0,0,,Let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.34,0:08:42.84,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,What if they start dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:42.84,Saku-overlap,JIN,0,0,0,,Let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.84,0:08:44.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,I'm asking you whether you'd mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.09,0:08:47.67,Saku-main,,0,0,0,,if Misaki-senpai gave all of \Nher being to another man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.39,0:08:50.68,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.68,0:08:52.99,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,Don't think you can say \Nwhatever you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:55.35,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,You're the one making me say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.69,0:09:00.43,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.55,0:09:07.10,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,Smart, mature, and dependable? \NWho are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:10.11,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,I couldn't take any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:12.99,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,I didn't even know if \NI'd get into college!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:15.11,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,I couldn't focus on anything \Nbecause of Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:19.10,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,It's not easy for me to confess \Nmy feelings to Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:21.45,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,I need to be prepared to spend \Nthe rest of my life with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.96,0:09:26.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,How can you say that when \Nyou've always been ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:36.97,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0,0,0,,Sorata, are you alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:38.79,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.04,0:09:42.47,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Listen, Shiina...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:44.18,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:46.48,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,I can almost see your panties.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.54,0:09:49.69,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0,0,0,,Don't look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:55.99,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,You've grown up a bit if you're \Nshamelessly looking up girls' skirts now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:09:58.20,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Jin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:09:59.99,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.31,0:10:02.96,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Why don't you stop this \Nif you like her so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:04.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Please go out with Misaki-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:07.48,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,Haven't you been listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:09.66,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0,0,0,,Misaki will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.66,0:10:11.80,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Aoyama went to get her. So, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:13.05,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,She won't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:13.55,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:16.07,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,She won't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:19.93,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,Kamiigusa-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:23.72,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,You're full of energy, Nanamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:26.43,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,Mitaka-senpai's at school right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:27.52,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.47,0:10:30.69,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:32.60,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,What? Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:33.98,Saku-main,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:36.57,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Because I'm finishing this right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:38.92,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Let's do it! I'm gonna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.21,0:10:43.06,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,Are you sure, Kamiigusa-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.88,0:10:45.79,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.04,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.03,0:10:53.13,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,You're the one who taught me \Nnot to hold my feelings in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:57.74,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,That's why I did my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.74,0:10:59.83,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,Senpai, are you going to do another...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.83,0:11:01.43,Saku-main,,0,0,0,,hundred laps around that same circle?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:03.30,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,I don't want to either,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:06.54,Saku-main,,0,0,0,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:17.18,Saku-thought,GIRL A,0,0,0,,Misaki-chan, you're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:19.21,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Jin, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.29,0:11:22.33,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,I was always with Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:25.58,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0,0,0,,It's snow! It's a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:26.81,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0,0,0,,It's a snowball fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.81,0:11:28.23,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Let's see who wants to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:29.81,Saku-thought,GIRL B,0,0,0,,I don't want to play if you're playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:30.72,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0,0,0,,What? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:32.46,Saku-thought,GIRL B,0,0,0,,Because we can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:32.46,Saku-overlap,GIRL C,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.93,0:11:35.37,Saku-thought,BOY A,0,0,0,,We'll beat Misaki today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.37,0:11:36.63,Saku-thought,BOY B,0,0,0,,Our pride depends on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:40.40,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,I thought Jin would \Nalways be by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:43.89,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Jin, it's morning! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:46.18,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0,0,0,,If you don't get up, I'm giving \Nyou a good morning kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.95,0:11:48.85,Saku-thought,JIN,0,0,0,,Okay, okay. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:51.27,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Hey, how do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:54.06,Saku-thought,JIN,0,0,0,,Don't do that outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:55.53,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.53,0:11:57.32,Saku-thought,FUUKA,0,0,0,,Because he doesn't want \Nother people to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:11:58.80,Saku-thought,JIN,0,0,0,,Fuuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:00.38,Saku-thought,FATHER,0,0,0,,Misaki, let's take a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:01.75,Saku-thought,MOTHER,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:03.35,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:07.91,Saku-thought,FUUKA,0,0,0,,Our parents get so excited \Nover everything Misaki does.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:10.00,Saku-thought,JIN,0,0,0,,And as her older sister, \Nyou're not happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.65,0:12:13.10,Saku-thought,FUUKA,0,0,0,,They even bought a new camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.53,0:12:15.51,Saku-thought,FUUKA,0,0,0,,Anyway, aren't you going to change?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:17.44,Saku-thought,JIN,0,0,0,,I was waiting for you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.18,0:12:20.78,Saku-thought,FUUKA,0,0,0,,How cheeky of you to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:21.72,Saku-thought,JIN,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.15,0:12:30.14,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Jin, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:33.55,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,I wonder whether...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.55,0:12:36.41,Saku-main,,0,0,0,,it would have been better if \NI'd realized how I felt sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:40.11,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0,0,0,,We've finished our first semester!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:43.06,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:43.06,Saku-overlap,GIRL A,0,0,0,,Look. How embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.06,0:12:46.08,Saku-thought,GIRL B,0,0,0,,I can't get my head around \Nthe fact she's a brainiac.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:46.49,Sign,SIGN,0,0,0,,Exam Results
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:46.49,Sign,SIGN,0,0,0,,1. Kamiigusa Misaki
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:47.99,Saku-thought,GIRL A,0,0,0,,Mitaka-kun, are you going home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:49.55,Saku-thought,GIRL B,0,0,0,,We're off to sing karaoke. \NDo you want to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:51.45,Saku-thought,GIRL B,0,0,0,,Some other girls from \Nour class are coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.19,0:12:54.21,Saku-thought,JIN,0,0,0,,Is there anyone cuter than her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:55.12,Saku-thought,GIRL A,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:57.03,Saku-thought,JIN,0,0,0,,I said I've got something \NI have to do today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:12:58.45,Saku-thought,GIRL B,0,0,0,,You're no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.45,0:13:00.67,Saku-thought,GIRL A,0,0,0,,Next time, then. Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:07.01,Saku-thought,SENPAI A,0,0,0,,She's kinda sexy, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:09.61,Saku-thought,SENPAI B,0,0,0,,Her personality's beyond belief, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.61,0:13:11.30,Saku-thought,SENPAI C,0,0,0,,I wonder if she'd let me—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:15.46,Saku-thought,SENPAI A,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:15.46,Saku-overlap,SENPAI B,0,0,0,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.89,0:13:20.90,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Yay! All done!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.41,0:13:23.20,Saku-thought,SENNIN,0,0,0,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:27.21,Saku-thought,TEACHER A,0,0,0,,Kamiigusa again? There's \Nnothing we can do about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.21,0:13:28.87,Saku-thought,TEACHER B,0,0,0,,You have your work \Ncut out with that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:32.29,Saku-thought,JIN,0,0,0,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:34.67,Saku-thought,JIN,0,0,0,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:37.15,Saku-thought,FUUKA,0,0,0,,Did you get in a fight again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:38.75,Saku-thought,FUUKA,0,0,0,,How many times is this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:38.75,Saku-overlap,FUUKA,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:40.69,Saku-thought,JIN,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Fuuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:48.75,Saku-thought,FUUKA,0,0,0,,Your heart's pounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:51.30,Saku-thought,JIN,0,0,0,,So is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:54.02,Saku-thought,FUUKA,0,0,0,,I can't watch this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.55,0:13:55.32,Saku-thought,JIN,0,0,0,,Watch what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.61,0:13:58.77,Saku-thought,FUUKA,0,0,0,,I can't watch Misaki hurt you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:00.51,Saku-thought,JIN,0,0,0,,I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:01.77,Saku-thought,FUUKA,0,0,0,,Your heart just leaped, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:06.57,Saku-thought,FUUKA,0,0,0,,I won't hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:14.72,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Maybe I wouldn't have been running\N in circles if I'd noticed sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:24.99,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Jin! Fuuka-chan! Welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:27.12,Saku-thought,FUUKA,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.89,0:14:29.32,Saku-thought,FATHER,0,0,0,,Time for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:31.44,Saku-thought,MOTHER,0,0,0,,Misaki, we made your favorite! Crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:33.39,Saku-thought,MOTHER,0,0,0,,Come and get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:33.12,Saku-overlap,JIN,0,0,0,,Your parents are calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:34.03,Saku-overlap,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:34.44,Saku-thought,FATHER,0,0,0,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:36.52,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,Misaki won't show.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:40.41,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,She's been avoiding me lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:43.64,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Huh? Avoiding... What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:47.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,But Misaki-senpai's feeling better now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:48.22,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:52.09,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,She won't answer her phone \Nand she doesn't answer my texts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:53.95,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,Misaki won't show.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:14:58.17,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,I'm too afraid to go see Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:01.72,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,I feel like I'd say \Nsomething mean if I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.72,0:15:02.50,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:06.49,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,I thought I might be able to see \Nhim after I finished this scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.93,0:15:08.76,Saku-main,,0,0,0,,but I just can't finish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:11.97,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,I don't want to finish it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:13.97,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:16.97,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0,0,0,,Misaki will still come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:19.14,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0,0,0,,Nanami will bring her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:25.84,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,I'm really glad I came to Suimei High.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:36.72,Saku-thought,JIN,0,0,0,,Do you want this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.34,0:15:39.75,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.99,0:15:43.34,Saku-thought,SENNIN,0,0,0,,There you are, Kamiigusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:44.85,Saku-thought,JIN,0,0,0,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.85,0:15:46.26,Saku-thought,SENNIN,0,0,0,,Oopsy-daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:48.89,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Did you come to deliver \Nyour last words, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:50.34,Saku-thought,SENNIN,0,0,0,,I'm not dying yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:51.69,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0,0,0,,You're going soft, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:53.00,Saku-thought,JIN,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:58.14,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Suimei University of \Nthe Arts High School?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:00.49,Saku-thought,SENNIN,0,0,0,,Listen, Kamiigusa:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:05.50,Saku-thought,SENNIN,0,0,0,,There are no aliens like \Nyou in this tiny town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:10.79,Saku-thought,SENNIN,0,0,0,,But if you go to that school, \Nyou might find others like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.79,0:16:15.20,Saku-thought,,0,0,0,,who have found their\N way onto this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:18.44,Saku-thought,SENNIN,0,0,0,,Why don't you try applying here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:20.15,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.86,0:16:29.92,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,That's when I realized \NMisaki knew she was alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:33.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Why did you apply to Suimei High?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.91,0:16:34.73,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.90,0:16:37.85,Saku-thought,JIN,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of applying to Suimei, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:40.66,Saku-thought,FUUKA,0,0,0,,That's not funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:43.85,Saku-thought,,0,0,0,,Leaving home and living in a dorm \Nsounds like fun, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.36,0:16:46.22,Saku-thought,JIN,0,0,0,,I'm kind of interested in \Nattending an art school, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:49.17,Saku-thought,FUUKA,0,0,0,,So you do prefer Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:52.03,Saku-thought,FUUKA,0,0,0,,You're always so worried about Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:53.87,Saku-thought,FUUKA,0,0,0,,Misaki's the only one you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:57.97,Saku-thought,FUUKA,0,0,0,,I thought you'd at least look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.22,0:17:03.22,Saku-thought,FUUKA,0,0,0,,I'm nothing more than a \NMisaki substitute to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:04.05,Saku-thought,JIN,0,0,0,,That's not—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.05,0:17:06.17,Saku-thought,FUUKA,0,0,0,,You're afraid you'll hurt Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:09.67,Saku-thought,FUUKA,0,0,0,,You want to keep her pure and \Nuntouched by your side forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:12.41,Saku-thought,FUUKA,0,0,0,,Isn't that why you're with me instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:21.93,Saku-thought,FUUKA,0,0,0,,At least make an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.34,0:17:28.08,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,I probably just couldn't ignore Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:36.39,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,Oh, that's it! I'm out of patience!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.39,0:17:37.61,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Nanamin?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:40.63,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,Mitaka-senpai's going \Nfar away this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.63,0:17:41.66,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,Is that okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:45.85,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,Leap into space!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:45.85,Saku-overlap,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Hey, Nanamin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.20,0:17:46.45,Sign,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Under Construction
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:52.96,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,I'm really glad I came to Suimei High.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:55.47,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,I'm glad I met you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:58.83,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,Knowing Misaki has people around her\N who will get angry for her sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:01.07,Saku-main,,0,0,0,,makes me extremely happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:02.23,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Jin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:06.39,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,She's definitely not going to show now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.91,0:18:16.17,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.92,0:18:18.81,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Aoyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.81,0:18:19.57,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:20.98,Saku-main,TEACHER A,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:22.26,Saku-main,TEACHER A,0,0,0,,We heard there was a fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:23.76,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0,0,0,,What are you doing on a \Ntest announcement day?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:23.76,Saku-main,TEACHER B,0,0,0,,There's an explanation for all of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:24.35,Saku-main,TEACHER A,0,0,0,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:25.44,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,I'm sure you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:25.99,Saku-overlap,TEACHER B,0,0,0,,Open this door, Kanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.99,0:18:26.89,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Jin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:28.54,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:30.21,Saku-main,TEACHER A,0,0,0,,I'm telling you to open this door!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:31.71,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Shiina, help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:33.92,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.69,0:18:38.47,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Run, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:44.97,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Are you pushing me? \NTickling me? Massaging me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:45.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:47.06,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0,0,0,,Which do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:47.90,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Push!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:48.85,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,Kamiigusa-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.87,0:18:51.58,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:54.26,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,What a bunch of meddling \Nunderclassmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:56.74,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it's not \Nso bad once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.09,0:18:58.82,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:00.43,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:04.73,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,I passed. I'm going to Osaka in April.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.97,0:19:06.96,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.61,0:19:10.83,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,So, Misaki, don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:13.15,Saku-main,,0,0,0,,Do what you really want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.66,0:19:18.30,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,You must have realized it \Nwhen we all worked on Nyapollon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:20.23,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,You had fun, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.23,0:19:25.35,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Yeah. Mashiron's work was amazing, \Nand every day was exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:28.31,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,The Dragon did everything \NI asked him to do, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:30.14,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,I had so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:34.77,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,Then, you know my scripts \Naren't good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:38.71,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,At least you're honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:41.98,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Your scripts \N{\i1}aren't{\i0} good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.44,0:19:44.48,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,They don't excite me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:48.74,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,You were disappointed every \Ntime I finished one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:50.38,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:53.84,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,Four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:57.65,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,Four years from now, \NI'll come back and write scripts...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:20:00.79,Saku-main,,0,0,0,,good enough to be \Nhired by Kamiigusa Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.31,0:20:03.33,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,So, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:08.88,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Wh-What—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:11.78,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,It'll keep men away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.46,0:20:13.27,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,If you don't want it, pitch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:14.98,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:19.92,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,I'll never take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.21,0:20:23.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.58,0:20:26.37,Saku-main,TEACHER A,0,0,0,,Come and join us in \Nthe faculty office for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:27.83,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,Does "a while" mean five minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:30.39,Saku-main,TEACHER B,0,0,0,,You're really going to get it today! \NPrepare yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:32.35,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:41.53,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,Thanks for the last three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.53,0:20:43.97,Saku-main,TEACHER A,0,0,0,,Hey! Mitaka, open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:45.98,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,You'll get in even more trouble later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:48.26,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,Sorata's the one who \Nwill get in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:49.40,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:51.82,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,Third years can come \Nand go as we please,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.82,0:20:53.44,Saku-main,,0,0,0,,and I won't be coming \Nto school tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:55.10,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,You had all of that worked out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:56.73,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:20:58.69,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Home?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.51,0:21:02.40,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,To Sakura Hall, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:03.69,Saku-main,ALL,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:06.50,Saku-main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.02,0:21:20.25,Saku-main,TEACHERS,0,0,0,,Open this door!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:23.97,Saku-main,TEACHERS,0,0,0,,Please open this door! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.43,0:21:27.89,Sign,SIGN,0,0,0,,There are people on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.43,0:21:27.89,Sign,SIGN,0,0,0,,Please look out for them while doing your rounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.12,0:22:50.49,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Nanamin! Mashiron! Look! Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.49,0:22:52.05,Saku-main,NANAMI,0,0,0,,That's great, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.69,0:22:53.61,Saku-main,,0,0,0,,It suits you perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.61,0:22:55.41,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,She really does seem happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.41,0:22:56.96,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,It took a long time to get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.96,0:22:59.34,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,What are you two talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.34,0:23:00.37,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,You scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.37,0:23:02.73,Saku-main,JIN,0,0,0,,We were wondering how far we can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.25,0:23:07.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,You can go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.17,0:23:10.27,Saku-main,MISAKI,0,0,0,,Kouhai-kun, that's some statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.27,0:23:13.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0,0,0,,Living in Sakura Hall \Nmakes you think like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.60,0:23:15.58,Sign,SIGN,0,0,0,,Sakura Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.63,0:23:16.47,Saku-main,ALL,0,0,0,,We're home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.74,0:23:21.58,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0,0,0,,Mitaka's here, too? Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.19,0:23:26.97,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0,0,0,,The board of trustees have decided \Nto demolish Sakura Hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.97,0:23:28.67,Saku-main,,0,0,0,,at the end of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.57,0:23:32.74,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0,0,0,,Hikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.74,0:23:35.87,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0,0,0,,What was Sakura Hall like \Nbefore I showed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.83,0:23:41.00,NextEptitle,TEXT,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1)}#19 There's No Place Like Sakura Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.87,0:23:37.76,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0,0,0,,"Our biscuits were soggy."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.76,0:23:40.54,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0,0,0,,"And Sorata was slouched over \Nlike a soggy biscuit." I see.
